First draft of README file
==========================

==================
To compile library
==================
On Linux and MacOS X platform :
$cd Build
$./bootstrap
$./configure --prefix=<path to install> --with-libARSalInstallDir=<path of libSAL install> --with-libARNetworkInstallDir=<path of libARNetwork install>
$make
$make install (if you want to install library)

On NDK Android platform :
$cd Build
$./bootstrap
$./configure --prefix=<path to install> --with-libARSalInstallDir=<path of libSAL install> --with-libARNetworkInstallDir=<path of libARNetwork install> --host=arm-linux-androideabi
$make
$make install (if you want to install library)

=================================
To generate doxygen documentation
=================================
$make doxygen-doc
